&lt;b>Сравнение версий &lt;a  href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RazdelPayments/FormaEditPayments&amp;amp;v=95x" class="">/Документация&amp;nbsp;IP&amp;nbsp;Studio&amp;nbsp;AMBS&amp;nbsp;/&amp;nbsp;Раздел&amp;nbsp;Payments&amp;nbsp;/&amp;nbsp;Форма&amp;nbsp;Edit&amp;nbsp;Payments&lt;/a> за &lt;a href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RazdelPayments/FormaEditPayments&amp;amp;time=2007-07-17+17%3A03%3A10">2007-07-17 17:03:10&lt;/a> и &lt;a href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RazdelPayments/FormaEditPayments&amp;amp;time=2007-07-17+17%3A05%3A28">2007-07-17 17:05:28&lt;/a>&lt;/b>&lt;br />
